item.title: Mail
item.description: Overview # ߷ This article is about Vekllei society The Royal Mail of Vekllei is perhaps the country’s most visible organisation overseas. For many foreigners, Royal Mail aircraft may be the closest they ever come to seeing for themselves the mysterious Atlantic country. For Vekllei residents, the ancient organisation is a living relic of the country’s ancient history, and an ongoing testament to the longevity of their people. The Royal Mail of Vekllei, referred to as the Mail or Mail A.
